# Rules of Engagement

Follow `docs/agents/rules-of-engagement.md` in full. Summary:

## Finish the task

When work changes files and the user has **not** opted out: commit, then push to `main`.

## Branches and worktrees

Work on `main` in the primary checkout unless the user asks for a separate branch or worktree.

## Asset generation

Use the built-in imagegen tool when available. Otherwise fall back to Codex image gen (`~/.claude/skills/codex-imagegen/imagegen.sh`). No API stubs or placeholder art.

## GitHub Pages

Every repo is hosted on GitHub Pages. Follow `docs/agents/github-pages.md`. Fix missing paths, deploy workflow, or README as part of the task.

## How to work

Minimize scope. Follow invoked skills. Prefix shell commands with `rtk`. Use domain docs from `CONTEXT-MAP.md`.
